   $v3 1
   @ARGV foo

T:
O: no_ignore_case
P: one \\$v1 One \\$v2 oNe \\$v3
A: -oNe -one foo
   $v1 1
   $v3 1
   @ARGV foo

T: No arguments allowed
P: one
A: --one= foo
W: Option one does not take an argument
   @ARGV foo

T: More than once
P: one \\$v1
A: -one -one foo
   $v1 1
   @ARGV foo

T: Negation
P: one! \\$v1
A: -one -noone foo
   $v1 0
   @ARGV foo

T: Negation with aliases 
P: one|two! \\$v1
A: -one -two foo
   $v1 1
   @ARGV foo

T: Aliases 
